dmca.title: Coral Calcium stiffens efforts against copied label
dmca.body:
Re: Coral Calcium Supreme Label Copyright Infringement
Email  [private]@cox.net



Certificate of Copyright Registration

WHEREAS, on 7/31/2006, Timothy Matson engaged the services of Click&Copyright (www.clickandcopyright.com) to register a copyright application with the U.S. Copyright Office; and

WHEREAS, on 7/31/2006, Click&Copyright received Coral Calcium Supreme Label (title of work filed with the U.S. Copyright Office) from Timothy Matson; and

WHEREAS, on 8/1/2006 Click&Copyright sent the copyright application, the $45 filing fee, and the work entitled 'Coral Calcium Supreme Label' to the U.S. Copyright Office via USPS Priority Delivery; and

WHEREAS, on 8/7/2006 the U.S. Copyright Office received delivery of Coral Calcium Supreme Label, the completed Copyright Application and the $45 federal filing fee. Said delivery can be confirmed at www.usps.com by entering the following tracking number: 0103 8555 7496 8949 4074; and

WHEREAS, pursuant to the Code of Federal Regulations, 37 CFR
